    "updated_at": "2014-10-21T22:17:27Z",
    "body": "An RFC could be filed about turning `cmp::max` / `cmp::min` into methods on an extension trait, but I don't think the specific suggestions here make sense. The reality of floating point is that it differs quite a bit from common expectations and it's not the role of the language to work around that.\n",
